Berg - doesn't appear to say.
Wilson, How to Rebuild - open end facing into the case, except for
  Autostick, where open end faces out.
Bentley '63-'67 - Cutaway on M-1 3 shows open end facing in.
  M-9 4 appears to show open end facing in.
  M-9 7 and M-15 7, lower right, appears to show open end facing in.
  M-15 4 appears to show open end facing in. 
  M-19 1 very clearly shows open end facing in.
Bentley '50-'62 - 1-3, 1-3, and M-1 3 clearly show open end facing in.
  9-2 clearly shows open end facing in.
  10-5 appears to show open end facing in.
  10-13 appears to show open end facing in.
  M-9 4 appears to show open end facing in.
  M-9 6 clearly shows open end facing in.
  M-9 7 clearly shows open end facing in.
  13-1 clearly shows the open end facing in.
  M 13-1 clearly shows the open end facing in.
The '54 parts book online shows the open end facing in.
The '67 parts book online shows the open end facing in.

